void edu::stanford::atom::sti::client::gui::tabbedplotter::TabbedPlotter::updateInputTextArea (  )  [inline, private]

If there is any active tab, set the input text area to the value from the Vector<String> corresponding to the functions plotted on that graph. Otherwise, if there is no active tab, set the input text area to null.
